title: Grateful Dead Live at Oakland Alameda County Coliseum Arena on 1991-10-27
lineage: Tascam 112 MKII (XLR Out)> Tascam HD-P2 @ 24/48>   HDD>Amadeus Pro (Tracking/Fades/FLAC8)
description:
Set 1

Jack Straw, They Love Each Other, Me & My Uncle-> Mexicali Blues, Dupree's Diamond Blues, CC Rider, Althea, Lazy Lightning-> Supplication-> Might As Well
